"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qdc1665702602510.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qdc1665702602510.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qdc1665702602510.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qdc1665702602510\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $fieldvalidation\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qdc1665702602510___fieldvalidation_265405\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Identify whether a field requires validation.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__topic_d83564e1_d83565e1_d83566e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__p_d83567e1_d83568e1_d83569e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldvalidation</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__topic_d55227e1_d55228e1_d55229e1_d55230e1_d55231e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d336281e75\">\n                       Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__d6203e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__d6203e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__d6203e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__d6203e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdc1665702602510__d6203e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdc1665702602510__d6203e20__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdc1665702602510__d6203e20__entry__3\">Field name. It can optionally contain a\n                        qualified field name, for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">MYFLD.MYENT</code>. If omitted,\n                        the current field is assumed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__topic_d55232e1_d55233e1_d55234e1_d55235e1_d55236e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d336281e132\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8609e1_d8610e1_d8611e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\"></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8609e1_d8610e1_d8611e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8609e1_d8610e1_d8611e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8609e1_d8610e1_d8611e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\"\"</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8609e1_d8610e1_d8611e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span>\n\t\tcontains the exact error.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8609e1_d8610e1_d8611e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8609e1_d8610e1_d8611e1__entry__2\">\n Field does not require validation because it has not been modified or it has already been successfully validated.\n <p class=\"p\">Check the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldmod</span> to determine which of these situations applies.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8609e1_d8610e1_d8611e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8609e1_d8610e1_d8611e1__entry__2\">\n Field requires validation.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8612e1_d8613e1_d8614e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following Field-Level ProcScript Functions</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8612e1_d8613e1_d8614e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8612e1_d8613e1_d8614e1__entry__2\">\nError\nconstant\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8612e1_d8613e1_d8614e1__entry__3\">\nMeaning\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8612e1_d8613e1_d8614e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1101\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8612e1_d8613e1_d8614e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_FIELD&gt;\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdc1665702602510__table_d8612e1_d8613e1_d8614e1__entry__3\">\nAn incorrect\nfield name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically\nor the field is not available in the component.\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__topic_d55237e1_d55238e1_d55239e1_d55240e1_d55241e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d336281e267\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__d6366e20\">Allowed in form and service components (and in report components that are not self-contained).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__topic_d55242e1_d55243e1_d55244e1_d55245e1_d55246e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d336281e277\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__p_d83585e1_d83586e1_d83587e1\">All fields of an entity can be validated. Data in a field needs validation in the following circumstances:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__li_d34295e1_d34296e1_d34297e1\">Data in the field has been modified (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldmod</span> is 1), but has not yet been successfully validated (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldvalidation</span> is also 1).\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__li_d34298e1_d34299e1_d34300e1\">Validation has been demanded by ProcScript (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldcheck</span> is 1), regardless of the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldvalidation</span>.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__section_k2h_cfz_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d336281e307\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldvalidation</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qdc1665702602510__pre_llr_cfz_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$MYFIELD$ = \"CUSTID.CUST\"\nif ( $fieldvalidation($MYFIELD$))\n...\nendif\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrk1665702576500.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Validate</a><p>Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwi1665702576586.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatefield</a><p>Validate a field of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swr1665702599962.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldcheck</a><p>Return or set the requirement for field validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rjy1665702601052.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldmod</a><p>Return the modification status of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aul1665702602685.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fielddbmod</a><p>Return the modification status of a database field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/biz1719502191613.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancevalidation</a><p>Identify whether data in the component instance requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcw1719485700746.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keyvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpz1719812992669.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occvalidation</a><p>Check whether an occurrence requires validation.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531203\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531203\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$fieldvalidation Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $fieldvalidation Identify whether a field requires validation. $fieldvalidation { ( Field ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Field String Field name. It can optionally contain a qualified field name, for example MYFLD.MYENT . If omitted, the current field is assumed. Return Values Table 2. Value Meaning \"\" An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. 0 Field does not require validation because it has not been modified or it has already been successfully validated. Check the value of $fieldmod to determine which of these situations applies. 1 Field requires validation. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following Field-Level ProcScript Functions Value Error constant Meaning -1101 <UPROCERR_FIELD> An incorrect field name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically or the field is not available in the component. Use Allowed in form and service components (and in report components that are not self-contained). Description All fields of an entity can be validated. Data in a field needs validation in the following circumstances: Data in the field has been modified ( $fieldmod is 1), but has not yet been successfully validated ( $fieldvalidation is also 1). Validation has been demanded by ProcScript ( $fieldcheck is 1), regardless of the value of $fieldvalidation . Example: Using $fieldvalidation $MYFIELD$ = \"CUSTID.CUST\" if ( $fieldvalidation($MYFIELD$)) ... endif Copy Related Links Validate Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default). validatefield Validate a field of the current occurrence. $fieldcheck Return or set the requirement for field validation. $fieldmod Return the modification status of a field. $fielddbmod Return the modification status of a database field. $instancevalidation Identify whether data in the component instance requires validation. $keyvalidation Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation. $occvalidation Check whether an occurrence requires validation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}